Chopping firewood, huh?

00:26:37.000 --> 00:26:38.700
Heard you're about to be a grandpa.

00:26:38.980 --> 00:26:39.920
Congratulations, congratulations!

00:26:40.500 --> 00:26:41.559
We haven't even attended

00:26:41.559 --> 00:26:42.559
Xiaofang's wedding yet.

00:26:42.880 --> 00:26:44.079
Are the wedding and the baby's one-month party

00:26:44.099 --> 00:26:44.960
Going to be held together?

00:26:45.140 --> 00:26:46.319
We'll pay double.

00:26:46.779 --> 00:26:47.119
Right.

00:26:47.599 --> 00:26:48.539
We'll give two gifts.

00:26:49.680 --> 00:26:51.700
I can't quite control my strength here.

00:26:52.720 --> 00:26:54.039
Watch out, something might fly off.

00:26:54.039 --> 00:26:54.740
Not the wood,

00:26:55.099 --> 00:26:56.019
But the axe.

00:26:57.059 --> 00:26:58.740
Whoever it hits is out of luck.

00:27:00.140 --> 00:27:01.400
Don't get blood all over yourself.

00:27:01.799 --> 00:27:02.819
Getting worked up already?

00:27:56.200 --> 00:27:56.640
Oh my God!

00:27:57.200 --> 00:27:58.720
Yang Fanhu's coming to hack someone!

00:27:59.539 --> 00:28:00.779
Where? Where is he?

00:28:07.019 --> 00:28:08.319
Is there no law anymore?

00:28:08.680 --> 00:28:09.940
You dare? Come on then!

00:28:10.019 --> 00:28:10.980
Let's see if you dare swing that!

00:28:12.640 --> 00:28:14.019
Your son's got such a dumb head,

00:28:14.019 --> 00:28:15.099
He takes right after you!

00:28:15.160 --> 00:28:16.420
You think Yang Fanhu's someone to mess with?

00:28:16.759 --> 00:28:17.359
When he's fuming mad,

00:28:17.359 --> 00:28:18.160
There's nothing he won't do!

00:28:18.799 --> 00:28:19.799
Back when his wife cheated on him,

00:28:19.799 --> 00:28:20.960
He nearly beat the guy to death!

00:28:21.200 --> 00:28:22.400
I was standing right there watching!

00:28:24.160 --> 00:28:24.779
Qi Xiaowei, you fool!

00:28:25.640 --> 00:28:26.819
You dared to mess with his daughter?

00:28:27.319 --> 00:28:28.380
Got a death wish or something?

00:28:28.779 --> 00:28:30.140
We... we didn't do anything wrong!

00:28:31.539 --> 00:28:32.680
We're in a serious relationship!

00:28:32.819 --> 00:28:33.940
You already knocked her up!

00:28:34.099 --> 00:28:35.099
Serious, my ass!

00:28:35.460 --> 00:28:36.980
He's already at the middle of the bridge!

00:28:37.779 --> 00:28:38.900
Hurry, block the door with something!

00:28:39.140 --> 00:28:39.500
Got it!

00:28:41.759 --> 00:28:42.640
She's not even married in yet,

00:28:42.980 --> 00:28:44.460
And it looks like they're about to brawl!

00:28:44.819 --> 00:28:46.500
These Butterfly Lovers of ours...

00:28:47.039 --> 00:28:47.759
These two families

00:28:48.059 --> 00:28:49.000
Never got along in the first place.

00:28:49.640 --> 00:28:50.759
But of all things, their kids

00:28:50.759 --> 00:28:51.480
Went and hooked up!

00:28:51.900 --> 00:28:53.559
So this whole mess? Real tricky now.

00:28:54.160 --> 00:28:55.400
Why did he stop moving?

00:28:56.660 --> 00:28:57.180
Where? Where is he?

00:29:09.299 --> 00:29:09.940
Uncle.

00:29:13.019 --> 00:29:14.279
Is Xiaofang back, Uncle?

00:29:16.140 --> 00:29:17.079
Let's go see her then.

00:29:17.720 --> 00:29:18.000
Let's go.

00:29:18.059 --> 00:29:18.299
Come on.

00:29:18.640 --> 00:29:19.160
Bye, Uncle.

00:29:21.900 --> 00:29:23.920
Xiaofang! Xiaofang!

00:29:25.859 --> 00:29:28.299
Come, let's go find Auntie Xiaofang.

00:29:28.460 --> 00:29:29.059
Okay?

00:29:31.000 --> 00:29:31.380
Careful.

00:29:31.380 --> 00:29:31.900
You're here!

00:29:32.180 --> 00:29:32.920
You're here!

00:29:33.299 --> 00:29:35.180
I missed you so much, Xiaofang.

00:29:35.819 --> 00:29:37.599
You didn't even come down to greet us.

00:29:37.599 --> 00:29:38.420
Seriously.

00:29:38.460 --> 00:29:39.559
Putting on airs, huh?

00:29:39.640 --> 00:29:39.960
Come.

00:29:40.500 --> 00:29:41.079
Take a look.

00:29:41.339 --> 00:29:41.980
Look at her belly.

00:29:41.980 --> 00:29:42.839
Oh my god.

00:29:43.660 --> 00:29:45.420
You're barely showing at all.

00:29:45.900 --> 00:29:46.740
When I was pregnant,

00:29:46.740 --> 00:29:47.700
My belly was huge.

00:29:48.460 --> 00:29:49.339
How does it feel?

00:29:49.900 --> 00:29:50.359
Take a guess.

00:29:50.420 --> 00:29:51.740
There's a little life in there.

00:29:51.740 --> 00:29:52.799
Let me touch for luck.

00:30:02.579 --> 00:30:04.400
Fanyan, put yourself in my shoes.

00:30:04.900 --> 00:30:06.079
If I don't stop her,

00:30:06.400 --> 00:30:08.099
She'll call my son back home.

00:30:08.220 --> 00:30:09.119
If he comes back,

00:30:09.240 --> 00:30:10.220
It'll mess up his studies,

00:30:10.500 --> 00:30:12.220
And the flight alone costs tens of thousands.

00:30:12.720 --> 00:30:14.200
I'm just trying to save money.

00:30:14.299 --> 00:30:15.460
You can't save that money.

00:30:16.319 --> 00:30:17.299
You already booked the flights.

00:30:17.759 --> 00:30:18.859
The hotel's already confirmed.

00:30:19.440 --> 00:30:20.579
I already cancelled it.

00:30:21.559 --> 00:30:22.619
Something this big,

00:30:23.180 --> 00:30:23.819
Why didn't you

00:30:23.819 --> 00:30:24.779
Discuss it with me first?

00:30:24.839 --> 00:30:26.019
You've always been reasonable.

00:30:26.079 --> 00:30:27.180
Cut it out with the

00:30:27.180 --> 00:30:27.859
Crocodile tears.

00:30:28.740 --> 00:30:30.099
I already told my mom

00:30:30.259 --> 00:30:31.660
I was going to the Maldives with you.

00:30:32.160 --> 00:30:32.640
Now how am I supposed

00:30:32.640 --> 00:30:33.519
To face my family?

00:30:34.759 --> 00:30:36.420
Just tell your mom you're not going.

00:30:37.400 --> 00:30:38.380
You think I'm like you?

00:30:38.500 --> 00:30:39.279
Going back on your word.

00:30:40.940 --> 00:30:41.460
Hello?

00:30:41.980 --> 00:30:42.440
Brother.

00:30:43.240 --> 00:30:44.140
Go ahead, what is it?

00:30:46.880 --> 00:30:47.720
Xiaofang...

00:30:48.680 --> 00:30:49.539
What about Xiaofang?

00:30:52.299 --> 00:30:53.140
She's pregnant.

00:30:53.980 --> 00:30:55.400
Xiaofang is pregnant.

00:30:56.140 --> 00:30:56.500
This...

00:30:57.680 --> 00:30:58.940
Drawing the curtains in broad daylight,

00:30:59.539 --> 00:31:00.740
Not even daring to fart out loud.

00:31:01.720 --> 00:31:03.000
How can we live like this?

00:31:03.819 --> 00:31:04.279
Oh mama.

00:31:04.359 --> 00:31:05.900
Keep your voice down, will you?

00:31:06.900 --> 00:31:08.660
You didn't used to be like this, Meimei.

00:31:09.579 --> 00:31:10.779
Well, you didn't used to be in debt either.

00:31:12.839 --> 00:31:13.460
Right, right, right.

00:31:14.180 --> 00:31:14.619
Then let's do this,

00:31:15.279 --> 00:31:16.220
Take our son

00:31:16.480 --> 00:31:17.579
Back to your parents' place to lay low.

00:31:18.140 --> 00:31:18.839
I'll handle things here.

00:31:19.400 --> 00:31:19.920
How can I go back?

00:31:20.420 --> 00:31:21.579
I don't have a single cent.

00:31:22.079 --> 00:31:23.279
You want me to go back and embarrass myself?

00:31:23.460 --> 00:31:24.160
I'll figure something out.

00:31:24.440 --> 00:31:24.920
Okay?

00:31:32.420 --> 00:31:32.859
Fan Mei.

00:31:33.319 --> 00:31:33.759
What is it?

00:31:34.420 --> 00:31:35.640
Xiaofang is pregnant before marriage.

00:31:35.779 --> 00:31:36.819
It's that Qi family boy's.

00:31:36.900 --> 00:31:37.619
What?

00:31:38.599 --> 00:31:39.900
Our brother didn't stab anyone, did he?

00:31:44.980 --> 00:31:45.900
Looks like reason

00:31:45.920 --> 00:31:47.559
Won out over that reckless outlaw in him.

00:32:08.980 --> 00:32:09.559
Where are you going?

00:32:20.259 --> 00:32:21.319
I'm going to the shop.

00:32:35.319 --> 00:32:37.279
It's dark. I'll go with you.

00:32:41.759 --> 00:32:43.880
Fine, I'm going to meet Xiaowei.

00:32:44.440 --> 00:32:45.259
You don't need to come.

00:32:46.579 --> 00:32:48.660
Whatever it is, tell him to come here.

00:32:48.920 --> 00:32:49.519
No, if you act like this,

00:32:49.519 --> 00:32:50.519
How would he dare come?

00:32:50.779 --> 00:32:52.599
He doesn't even have the guts

00:32:53.619 --> 00:32:55.019
To marry my daughter!

00:33:01.460 --> 00:33:02.500
Alright.

00:33:02.700 --> 00:33:04.099
Then I won't go.

00:33:04.200 --> 00:33:05.099
Okay?

00:33:09.240 --> 00:33:09.559
Alright.

00:33:10.200 --> 00:33:10.960
I'm going back to sleep.

00:33:11.059 --> 00:33:11.940
You get some sleep early too.

00:33:31.359 --> 00:33:33.259
Xiaowei, I can't get out.

00:33:33.359 --> 00:33:34.680
Come over here if you wanna talk.

00:33:35.759 --> 00:33:36.440
Xiaofang.

00:33:37.180 --> 00:33:37.640
Xiaofang.

00:33:43.500 --> 00:33:44.279
Are you okay?

00:33:52.299 --> 00:33:54.000
I'm fine. I saw it coming.

00:33:54.299 --> 00:33:55.099
What about your family?

00:33:57.220 --> 00:33:58.299
My parents chewed me out.

00:33:59.019 --> 00:34:00.640
But why does everyone else get to judge me?

00:34:00.859 --> 00:34:02.339
Their mouths belong to them.

00:34:02.460 --> 00:34:03.940
We can't stop them from talking.

00:34:04.980 --> 00:34:06.319
No way, I'm the man here.

00:34:06.319 --> 00:34:06.779
I've gotta do something.

00:34:07.880 --> 00:34:09.119
Is this a guy-girl thing now?

00:34:12.719 --> 00:34:13.920
Big cities are better after all.

00:34:14.260 --> 00:34:15.400
Nobody knows us here.

00:34:17.579 --> 00:34:19.039
We'll have to face it sooner or later.

00:34:19.900 --> 00:34:21.199
But as long as we stick together,

00:34:21.199 --> 00:34:22.199
We've got nothing to fear.

00:34:23.320 --> 00:34:24.460
Everything will be just fine.

00:34:24.900 --> 00:34:25.519
Whatever you say.

00:34:26.940 --> 00:34:27.780
It's the sweet and bitter of life.

00:34:27.940 --> 00:34:28.760
We can't have all the sweetness

00:34:28.760 --> 00:34:29.920
All to ourselves.

00:34:30.260 --> 00:34:30.619
Right.

00:34:31.099 --> 00:34:32.739
But I'm feeling pretty sweet right now.

00:34:35.599 --> 00:34:36.119
Give me a kiss.

00:34:38.719 --> 00:34:39.400
Come on, kiss me.

00:34:46.219 --> 00:34:46.940
Why're you running off?

00:35:01.280 --> 00:35:02.059
Why'd you scare him?

00:35:05.840 --> 00:35:06.719
Did I scare him?

00:35:35.179 --> 00:35:35.679
What are you screaming for?

00:35:36.460 --> 00:35:37.280
Did I scare you?

00:35:44.719 --> 00:35:45.219
Eighty-six.

00:35:49.360 --> 00:35:50.480
Let me check these pears, looks like...

00:35:51.719 --> 00:35:52.440
Look, sis.

00:35:52.760 --> 00:35:53.659
This one's not bad.

00:35:53.780 --> 00:35:54.659
It doesn't look good though.

00:35:54.679 --> 00:35:55.300
Let me take out a few.

00:35:56.300 --> 00:35:56.679
I don't want them.

00:35:57.980 --> 00:35:58.900
That's about right, enough.

00:35:59.619 --> 00:36:00.199
How much now?

00:36:00.760 --> 00:36:01.380
Seventy-two.

00:36:06.980 --> 00:36:07.659
These nectarines...

00:36:08.039 --> 00:36:08.559
Yeah.

00:36:08.860 --> 00:36:10.179
My mom likes fuzzy peaches.

00:36:10.420 --> 00:36:11.380
Let me pour them back, okay?

00:36:11.739 --> 00:36:12.460
I'll pour them back, sis.

00:36:13.380 --> 00:36:13.880
Save a bag.

00:36:14.360 --> 00:36:15.280
Thanks, thanks sis.

00:36:32.079 --> 00:36:32.860
You're back.

00:36:33.539 --> 00:36:33.960
Bro.

00:36:34.219 --> 00:36:35.559
Mom said you weren't coming back.

00:36:36.260 --> 00:36:37.420
I missed you two, that's all.

00:36:37.920 --> 00:36:38.380
Where's Mom?

00:36:38.800 --> 00:36:40.019
She went to Great-Grandma Seven's place.

00:36:51.239 --> 00:36:51.719
Second Sis.

00:36:53.880 --> 00:36:54.440
Big Sis.

00:37:07.679 --> 00:37:08.619
Those two in the same car?

00:37:09.059 --> 00:37:09.659
Wouldn't they fight?

00:37:10.219 --> 00:37:10.619
Bro.

00:37:12.179 --> 00:37:12.500
Bro.

00:37:12.900 --> 00:37:13.260
Bro.

00:37:13.679 --> 00:37:14.679
You came back so soon.

00:37:15.280 --> 00:37:16.000
With something this big going down,

00:37:16.219 --> 00:37:17.059
How could I not come back?

00:37:19.039 --> 00:37:19.659
What happened?

00:37:19.940 --> 00:37:21.059
Hurry, go grab the luggage from the car.

00:37:24.139 --> 00:37:25.059
What happened?

00:37:28.139 --> 00:37:28.780
Xiaofang.

00:37:29.320 --> 00:37:30.519
Your legs are really something.

00:37:30.579 --> 00:37:31.719
Being pregnant

00:37:31.719 --> 00:37:32.579
Hasn't slowed you down one bit.

00:37:34.219 --> 00:37:34.920
Xiaofang,

00:37:35.260 --> 00:37:36.440
You're the impressive one.

00:37:36.719 --> 00:37:38.079
If this happened to me,

00:37:38.340 --> 00:37:39.619
My dad would be furious.

00:37:40.460 --> 00:37:41.719
Xiaowei and I came back this time

00:37:41.719 --> 00:37:42.820
Planning to get married anyway.

00:37:43.360 --> 00:37:44.780
Getting pregnant was just a matter of time.

00:37:45.280 --> 00:37:47.340
Plus, Grandma and Dad have got my back.

00:37:48.119 --> 00:37:49.500
Uncle Hu is really good to you.

00:37:49.579 --> 00:37:50.380
Right?

00:37:51.039 --> 00:37:52.079
Every time I come back,

00:37:52.280 --> 00:37:53.340
My dad comes ahead of time

00:37:53.360 --> 00:37:54.559
To clean the place for me.

00:37:57.440 --> 00:37:57.980
Welcome back.

00:37:57.980 --> 00:37:59.340
I noticed Grandma's knees

00:37:59.340 --> 00:38:00.280
And my dad's back injury,

00:38:00.280 --> 00:38:01.679
Those old problems are getting worse.

00:38:02.139 --> 00:38:02.800
I need to find some

00:38:02.800 --> 00:38:04.000
Chuan Niu Xi and Drynaria rhizome.

00:38:04.739 --> 00:38:06.440
Qi Xiaowei is really lucky

00:38:06.480 --> 00:38:06.960
To have snagged

00:38:06.960 --> 00:38:08.239
Someone as capable as Xiaofang.

00:38:09.239 --> 00:38:10.199
Ever since Xiaowei and Xiaofang

00:38:10.199 --> 00:38:11.400
Got together,

00:38:11.599 --> 00:38:12.960
So many boys in our village

00:38:12.960 --> 00:38:13.599
Had their hearts broken.

00:38:13.639 --> 00:38:14.539
No kidding.

00:38:14.659 --> 00:38:15.539
How did such a beautiful flower

00:38:15.579 --> 00:38:17.260
End up being picked by Qi Xiaowei?

00:38:17.519 --> 00:38:18.579
Xiaofang coming back this time,

00:38:18.619 --> 00:38:20.219
The whole village is buzzing about it.

00:38:20.599 --> 00:38:21.659
Who knows what Qi Xiaowei

00:38:21.659 --> 00:38:22.619
Is even thinking.

00:38:22.619 --> 00:38:24.380
Young folks these days are so open-minded.

00:38:24.840 --> 00:38:26.480
If you ask me about this whole thing,

00:38:26.719 --> 00:38:27.480
The shame of it

00:38:27.480 --> 00:38:28.940
Is a complete and utter disgrace.

00:38:28.980 --> 00:38:30.440
Thank God she's not my wife.

00:38:31.119 --> 00:38:31.639
What a joke.

00:38:31.940 --> 00:38:32.760
Xiaowei's here.

00:38:32.920 --> 00:38:33.500
Get me a beer.

00:38:33.960 --> 00:38:34.320
You got it.

00:38:36.739 --> 00:38:37.119
Look at that.

00:38:40.860 --> 00:38:41.360
Xiaowei.

00:38:41.739 --> 00:38:42.340
Xiaowei's here.

00:38:43.800 --> 00:38:44.179
Come on.

00:38:44.480 --> 00:38:45.960
Xiaowei has always cared about his pride.

00:38:46.480 --> 00:38:48.079
The rumors going around the village are so ugly.

00:38:48.280 --> 00:38:49.219
Can he really take it?

00:38:49.800 --> 00:38:51.300
Who cares if he can take it or not.

00:38:51.420 --> 00:38:53.400
I think Xiaofang's the one getting the short end.

00:38:53.679 --> 00:38:54.619
You have no idea

00:38:54.659 --> 00:38:56.519
How hard it is to find a wife these days.

00:38:56.920 --> 00:38:58.159
Being hard is a good thing.

00:38:58.280 --> 00:39:00.599
Only then does true love really show.

00:39:01.039 --> 00:39:01.940
None of that stuff is hard.

00:39:02.260 --> 00:39:03.059
What's hard is that right now,

00:39:03.059 --> 00:39:04.099
I don't have any Chuan Niu Xi.

00:39:04.639 --> 00:39:06.260
So you two are coming up the mountain with me.

00:39:15.679 --> 00:39:16.619
What on earth happened?

00:39:16.900 --> 00:39:17.659
Am I invisible to you?

00:39:18.599 --> 00:39:19.119
Where's Xiaofang?

00:39:28.119 --> 00:39:29.219
Where are you going?

00:39:30.500 --> 00:39:31.360
I bet

00:39:32.059 --> 00:39:33.719
That punk took her off again.

00:39:34.820 --> 00:39:35.380
I'll go check.

00:39:36.739 --> 00:39:37.179
No way.

00:39:37.619 --> 00:39:38.199
Don't do anything rash.

00:39:38.480 --> 00:39:39.480
What do you mean, sis?

00:39:39.960 --> 00:39:40.579
No matter what,

00:39:40.659 --> 00:39:41.900
She still has to marry into their family.

00:39:42.179 --> 00:39:43.539
We can't cause a scene now.

00:39:43.760 --> 00:39:44.800
Marry who? Fight with who?

00:39:44.840 --> 00:39:45.840
Stay out of this. Shut up.

00:39:46.780 --> 00:39:47.340
Brother,

00:39:47.639 --> 00:39:49.260
Think about Xiaofang for once.

00:39:49.559 --> 00:39:50.099
This situation,

00:39:50.320 --> 00:39:51.739
We can't push it to the breaking point.

00:39:52.679 --> 00:39:53.559
What's going on, sis?

00:39:54.360 --> 00:39:56.380
Are you dense? Haven't you figured it out?

00:39:56.659 --> 00:39:58.239
Xiaofang is pregnant.

00:39:58.519 --> 00:39:59.340
What the hell?

00:40:00.079 --> 00:40:00.860
It's Qi Xiaowei's.

00:40:01.659 --> 00:40:03.019
You two keep an eye out.

00:40:03.420 --> 00:40:04.119
I'll go over and see.

00:40:05.599 --> 00:40:06.260
Xiaofang.

00:40:06.440 --> 00:40:08.179
Your two families have always had a feud.

00:40:08.239 --> 00:40:09.800
Could this marriage thing

00:40:09.900 --> 00:40:10.900
Turn into a brawl?

00:40:11.500 --> 00:40:12.380
How could it?

00:40:12.639 --> 00:40:13.739
Marriage is a good thing.

00:40:14.179 --> 00:40:14.800
Once they're married,

00:40:14.840 --> 00:40:16.380
We'll be long-standing family friends.

00:40:24.659 --> 00:40:25.500
Qiu Mei.

00:40:26.760 --> 00:40:27.559
Don't call me Qiu Mei.

00:40:30.980 --> 00:40:32.099
Fan...

00:40:32.639 --> 00:40:33.179
Fan...

00:40:34.219 --> 00:40:35.260
Yang Fanyan.

00:40:36.679 --> 00:40:37.539
Can't remember me?

00:40:38.579 --> 00:40:39.420
Don't recognize me?

00:40:40.559 --> 00:40:41.440
When did you get back?

00:40:41.920 --> 00:40:42.639
Just now.

00:40:43.139 --> 00:40:43.739
Have you eaten?

00:40:44.500 --> 00:40:45.139
Not yet.

00:40:46.179 --> 00:40:46.760
I came over

00:40:46.780 --> 00:40:47.360
Because I want to talk with you.

00:40:47.360 --> 00:40:48.280
Then hurry up and eat.

00:40:48.619 --> 00:40:49.480
I haven't cooked yet.

00:40:49.579 --> 00:40:50.440
I've got to go make dinner.

00:40:58.340 --> 00:40:58.800
Aunt!

00:40:59.019 --> 00:41:00.500
Xiaowei, run!

00:41:00.639 --> 00:41:01.840
The whole Yang family is here.

00:41:01.840 --> 00:41:02.880
We're gonna lose this one.

00:41:03.320 --> 00:41:03.900
Hurry up!

00:41:05.699 --> 00:41:06.940
Where do you think you're running?

00:41:06.980 --> 00:41:08.119
Hey, why are you grabbing me?

00:41:08.699 --> 00:41:09.820
Would I grab you if you weren't running?

00:41:10.199 --> 00:41:11.019
Would I run if you weren't grabbing me?

00:41:11.320 --> 00:41:12.460
Don't get smart with me.

00:41:12.519 --> 00:41:13.500
Tell me, where's Xiaofang?

00:41:13.619 --> 00:41:14.460
How would I know?

00:41:14.460 --> 00:41:15.380
We're not even together.

00:41:15.460 --> 00:41:16.579
Not together, huh?

00:41:16.639 --> 00:41:17.800
Don't even think about running.

00:41:17.980 --> 00:41:18.559
I'm asking you.

00:41:18.800 --> 00:41:19.980
What are you gonna do about Xiaofang?

00:41:20.280 --> 00:41:20.780
Do about what?

00:41:21.039 --> 00:41:22.579
Let me pull my pants up first!

00:41:22.599 --> 00:41:24.139
So you're just gonna hit and run?

00:41:24.320 --> 00:41:25.719
Yang Fanyan, don't push us around.

00:41:25.820 --> 00:41:26.440
What are you trying to do?

00:41:26.940 --> 00:41:27.719
It was your family's

00:41:27.719 --> 00:41:28.679
Yang Xiaofang who came on to him.

00:41:28.739 --> 00:41:29.800
You've got the nerve to say that?

00:41:29.900 --> 00:41:30.559
Stop, stop, stop!

00:41:30.920 --> 00:41:31.400
No digging here!

00:41:34.260 --> 00:41:34.679
What's the problem?

00:41:34.719 --> 00:41:35.699
This whole area,

00:41:36.019 --> 00:41:36.780
This whole patch,

00:41:36.840 --> 00:41:38.179
We planted the seeds here.

00:41:38.199 --> 00:41:39.059
Planted right here.

00:41:39.260 --> 00:41:41.400
Get out, get out, move along!

00:41:41.420 --> 00:41:42.139
Hold on.

00:41:42.539 --> 00:41:43.460
There's no sign saying

00:41:43.460 --> 00:41:44.500
This belongs to your family.

00:41:44.860 --> 00:41:45.719
Besides,

00:41:46.139 --> 00:41:47.679
Our village lives off the mountain.

00:41:48.039 --> 00:41:49.860
Everyone digs herbs on their own skill.

00:41:50.619 --> 00:41:51.500
Exactly.

00:41:51.820 --> 00:41:53.500
Xiaofang's grandpa was an herb hunter.

00:41:53.599 --> 00:41:54.960
She's roamed these hills since age four.

00:41:55.260 --> 00:41:55.760
Xiaofang.

00:41:56.199 --> 00:41:57.619
Ever seen anyone snatching herbs like this?

00:41:58.019 --> 00:41:58.760
Never.

00:41:58.940 --> 00:42:00.519
Never seen anyone so shameless.

00:42:00.599 --> 00:42:01.239
You... let go!

00:42:01.239 --> 00:42:02.400
Hey, stop!

00:42:02.800 --> 00:42:03.559
Say that one more time.

00:42:03.679 --> 00:42:04.079
Say what?

00:42:04.079 --> 00:42:04.639
I dare you to say it again.

00:42:04.639 --> 00:42:05.119
Stop, Qiu Mei.

00:42:05.519 --> 00:42:06.340
If you keep talking nonsense,

00:42:06.340 --> 00:42:07.480
I'll rip your mouth off.

00:42:07.500 --> 00:42:08.679
Mom, stop, they outnumber us.

00:42:08.679 --> 00:42:09.119
Just drop it.

00:42:09.559 --> 00:42:10.079
What's there to be afraid of?

00:42:10.400 --> 00:42:11.380
The Yang family

00:42:11.400 --> 00:42:12.559
Is all here today.

00:42:13.000 --> 00:42:13.900
Yang Xiaofang

00:42:14.099 --> 00:42:14.980
Is not someone your Qi family

00:42:14.980 --> 00:42:15.840
Can just push around.

00:42:16.139 --> 00:42:17.699
Our family isn't a pushover either.

00:42:18.079 --> 00:42:19.500
Yang Xiaofang started it.

00:42:19.820 --> 00:42:20.760
Absolutely shameless.

00:42:20.760 --> 00:42:21.860
Who are you calling shameless?

00:42:21.960 --> 00:42:22.579
Hey, stop it!

00:42:22.760 --> 00:42:23.639
You think I won't

00:42:23.920 --> 00:42:25.480
Chop you up and make soup out of you?

00:42:25.679 --> 00:42:27.159
Yang Fanhu's daughter,

00:42:27.300 --> 00:42:28.400
Your dad doesn't say a word,

00:42:28.519 --> 00:42:30.079
But you sure are sharp-tongued.

00:42:31.500 --> 00:42:33.219
No wonder you look so familiar.

00:42:34.340 --> 00:42:36.699
I never heard the Yang girl got married.

00:42:38.440 --> 00:42:41.000
You're carrying a bastard child, aren't you?

00:42:42.460 --> 00:42:43.900
A useless punk like Qi Xiaowei,

00:42:44.099 --> 00:42:45.179
Our Xiaofang making a move on him?

00:42:45.179 --> 00:42:46.179
That'd be the day.

00:42:46.219 --> 00:42:46.760
Hey, you!

00:42:47.940 --> 00:42:48.460
Who's a punk?

00:42:48.659 --> 00:42:49.400
How am I a punk?

00:42:49.460 --> 00:42:50.840
Xiaofang was the one who liked me first.

00:42:55.880 --> 00:42:57.900
Belly's out, and you won't stay home?

00:42:57.960 --> 00:42:59.400
Afraid nobody would notice?

00:42:59.639 --> 00:43:01.260
Go ahead, shout it all over the mountain!

00:43:01.380 --> 00:43:03.400
Pregnant without being married,

00:43:04.239 --> 00:43:05.920
Have you no shame?

00:43:07.659 --> 00:43:08.860
Is it shameful?

00:43:09.099 --> 00:43:10.800
I, Yang Xiaofang, didn't steal or rob.

00:43:10.800 --> 00:43:12.119
I got pregnant, proud and open.

00:43:12.260 --> 00:43:12.980
Is that shameful?

00:43:19.219 --> 00:43:19.699
She, she, she...

00:43:19.900 --> 00:43:21.280
Has she no shame?

00:43:21.360 --> 00:43:21.920
What's she doing?

00:43:22.500 --> 00:43:23.139
No idea.

00:43:25.079 --> 00:43:27.059
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant!

00:43:27.480 --> 00:43:28.519
Is that shameful?

00:43:29.179 --> 00:43:29.960
What is she doing?

00:43:30.219 --> 00:43:31.340
She's really shouting it out!

00:43:31.340 --> 00:43:31.840
Right?

00:43:39.940 --> 00:43:40.579
Yang Fanhu!

00:43:41.059 --> 00:43:41.960
Xiaowei, run!

00:43:42.340 --> 00:43:43.760
You wanna go back to jail again?

00:43:45.880 --> 00:43:46.639
Stop right there!

00:43:46.920 --> 00:43:47.539
Stop!

00:43:47.860 --> 00:43:48.460
Don't run!

00:43:49.039 --> 00:43:50.639
Xiaowei, run!

00:43:51.219 --> 00:43:51.940
Stop!

00:43:51.940 --> 00:43:52.659
Xiaowei!

00:43:53.000 --> 00:43:54.039
Run!

00:43:56.940 --> 00:43:57.599
Stop!

00:43:57.920 --> 00:43:58.880
Qi Xiaowei!

00:43:58.880 --> 00:43:59.679
Stop right there!

00:43:59.780 --> 00:44:00.559
Don't you run!

00:44:00.659 --> 00:44:02.059
My pants are falling down!

00:44:02.480 --> 00:44:03.239
Stop chasing him!

00:44:03.900 --> 00:44:04.760
Xiaowei!

00:44:05.380 --> 00:44:06.380
Run!

00:44:12.900 --> 00:44:15.440
I'm with Xiaowei. Is that shameful?

00:44:16.480 --> 00:44:19.320
I live my own way. Is that shameful?

00:44:20.099 --> 00:44:22.460
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant!

00:44:23.119 --> 00:44:24.199
Is that shameful?

00:44:26.900 --> 00:44:29.159
If I can birth this child, I can raise it.

00:44:29.639 --> 00:44:32.260
I'll own up to my own choices.

00:44:32.880 --> 00:44:33.960
Is that shameful?

00:44:35.860 --> 00:44:38.280
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant!

00:44:38.860 --> 00:44:40.059
Is that shameful?

00:44:42.920 --> 00:44:44.659
I, Yang Xiaofang...

00:44:45.119 --> 00:44:46.239
Am pregnant!

00:44:47.280 --> 00:44:48.780
It's not shameful!

00:45:05.739 --> 00:45:07.280
Of all the people you could've picked,

00:45:07.699 --> 00:45:09.599
You had to fall for Qi Xiaowei next door.

00:45:09.719 --> 00:45:10.599
Not even married yet,

00:45:10.599 --> 00:45:11.840
And she's already ditching us.

00:45:11.920 --> 00:45:12.880
You and Xiaofang used to be

00:45:12.880 --> 00:45:13.960
Childhood sweethearts, sure.

00:45:14.079 --> 00:45:15.019
But look at it now.

00:45:15.739 --> 00:45:17.420
One road split the two families apart.

00:45:17.539 --> 00:45:18.820
People change.

00:45:19.139 --> 00:45:19.860
Who's that?

00:45:20.039 --> 00:45:20.440
Yeah.

00:45:22.159 --> 00:45:23.800
Looks like Yang Xiaofang.

00:45:25.639 --> 00:45:27.260
If you ask me, Yang Xiaofang

00:45:27.280 --> 00:45:28.320
Can't stay in this village anymore.

00:45:30.559 --> 00:45:31.559
The wind's picking up.

00:45:33.820 --> 00:45:35.260
A storm is coming.

